entry.title: zendesk/sdk_messaging_ios
entry.summary:
The Zendesk Messaging SDK

⚠ Use of this software is subject to important terms and conditions as set forth in the License file ⚠

ZendeskSDKMessaging for iOS

The ZendeskSDKMessaging is an SDK that provides customer support through a Messaging interface powered by Zendesk Sunshine Conversations.

Documentation

You can find our documentation on https://developer.zendesk.com/embeddables/docs/zendesk-sdk-for-ios/getting_started.

API reference documentation

You can check the API documentation for Swift and Objective-C. In addition, a DocCArchive is also attached to every GitHub release. Download the file, open it and Xcode will add it to the Imported Documentation section of the documentation viewer.

Feature requests and issues

All feature requests and issues are welcomed. Please see our contributing guidelines to find out how to contact us.
